        <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
          <h2 class="display-5 fw-bold text-primary">Why Study in Ireland?</h2>
          <p class="lead">Ireland offers a unique blend of rich cultural heritage, cutting-edge research facilities, and a welcoming atmosphere for international students. With its world-renowned universities, English-speaking environment, and strong ties to global industries, Ireland provides an excellent platform for academic growth and career development.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <img src="/user-assets/img/destinations/irelandOverview.jpg" alt="Ireland Overview" class="img-fluid rounded">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Facts Section -->
  <section class="py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Key Facts about Ireland</h2>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Education System</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Ireland's education system is renowned for its excellence, particularly in sciences, technology, engineering, and literature. The country's universities consistently rank among the top 3% globally.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Innovation Hub</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Ireland is a leading global hub for innovation and technology. Many of the world's top companies in IT, pharmaceuticals, and finance have their European headquarters in Ireland.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Quality of Life</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Ireland offers a high quality of life with its beautiful landscapes, rich culture, and friendly people. It's consistently ranked as one of the safest countries in the world for international students.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Top Universities Section -->
  <section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
